[h1]The Elseif Statement [/h1]

[b]For example:[/b] [code format="php" codeId="477"]<?php
$age = 21;

[b]if[/b] ($age<=13) {
   echo "Child.";
} [b]elseif [/b]($age>13 && $age<19) {
   echo "Teenager";
} [b]else [/b]{
   echo "Adult";
}

//Outputs "Adult"
?>[/code]
[note]We used the [b]logical AND[/b] (&&) operator to combine the two conditions and check to determine whether $age is between 13 and 19.[/note]
